Hindi: No Not at all - नहीं, कभी नहीं
Tamil: No Not at all - இல்லை இல்லவே இல்லை
Telugu: No Not at all - అది కానే కాదు
Bangla: No Not at all - না কখনো না
Assamese - Ahomia: No Not at all - মুথেও নহয়

Tamil: Yes Most of the time -  ஆம், நாள் முழுதும் வேலை செய்கிறார்கள்
Telugu: Yes Most of the time - అవును ఎక్కువ సమయం

Hindi: Graduation and above -  स्नातक और उससे ऊपर
Telugu: Graduation and above - డిగ్రీ / పట్టభద్రుడు (బిఎ/బిఎస్‌సి/బికాం .... మొదలగు)
Bangla: Graduation and above - স্নাতক এবং উপরে
Odiya: Graduation and above - ଗ୍ରାଜୁଏଟ୍ ଏବଂ ଅଧିକ

Question Name: Reason for not in school - primary reason
Choice Text: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation
Kannada: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - ಕೆಲಸದಲ್ಲಿ ಕುಟುಂಬಕ್ಕೆ ಸಹಾಯ ಮಾಡಬೇಕಿದೆ/ಕೌಟುಂಬಿಕ ಉದ್ಯೋಗ
Hindi: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - काम में परिवार की मदद की आवश्यकता/घरेलू व्यवसाय
Tamil: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - குடும்பத்தினருக்கு வேலையில் உதவுதல்/வீட்டு வேலை
Telugu: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation -  కుటుంబమునకు సహాయపడటానికి (పనులకు) / కుటుంబ వృత్తికి తోడ్పడటానికి
Bangla: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - পরিবারের সাহায্য প্রয়োজন
Odiya: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - ପରିବାରକୁ କାମରେ ସହାଯ୍ୟ କରିବା ଦରକାର/ ପରିବାରର ପେଶା
Assamese - Ahomia: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - ঘৰত কাম কৰিব লাগে/ঘৰুৱা বৃত্তিত সহায়ৰ কাৰণে

Question Name: Reason for not in school - primary reason
Choice Text: Child need to work to earn money (labour work)
Kannada: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - ಹಣ ಸಂಪಾದಿಸಲು ಮಗುವು ಕೆಲಸ ಮಾಡಬೇಕಿರುವ ಅವಶ್ಯಕತೆ (ಕೂಲಿ ಕೆಲಸ)
Hindi: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - पैसा कमाने के लिये बच्चे को काम करना पड़ता है (बाल श्रम)
Tamil: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - குழந்தைத் தொழிலாளர்
Telugu: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) -  పిల్లలు కుటుంబ సంపాదన కొరకు పనిచేయాలి (కూలీ ప నులకు)
Bangla: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - শিশুকে অর্থ উপার্জন করতে হবে
Odiya: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - ଅର୍ଥ ଉପାର୍ଜନ ପାଇଁ ଶିଶୁ ଯଦି କାମ କରିବାକୁ ଚାହୁଁଛି
Assamese - Ahomia: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - উপাৰ্জন কৰিবলৈ কাম কৰিব লাগে

Question Name: Reason for not in school - primary reason
Choice Text: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other
Kannada: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - ಕೆಲಸಕ್ಕಾಗಿ ಅಥವಾ ಬೇರೆ ಉದ್ದೇಶಕ್ಕಾಗಿ ಕುಟುಂಬ/ಮಗುವು ಬೇರೆಡೆಗೆ ವಲಸೆ ಹೋಗಿರುವುದು
Hindi: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - परिवार/बच्चे को काम के लिये दूसरी जगह विस्थापित होना पड़ा या किसी अन्य कारण से
Tamil: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - குடும்பம்/குழந்தை வேலைக்காக அல்லது வேறு நோக்கத்திற்காக இடம்பெயர்ந்து சென்றது
Telugu: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other -  కుటుంబము / పిల్లలు  పనులు/సంపాదన/ఇతర కారణము తో ఇతర ప్రాంతములకు వలస వెళ్ళినారు
Odiya: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - ପରିବାର/ ଶିଶୁ କାମ ପାଇଁ କିମ୍ବା ଅନ୍ୟ କୌଣସି କାରଣ ପାଇଁ ଅନ୍ୟ ସ୍ଥାନକୁ ସ୍ଥାନାନ୍ତର ହୋଇ ଯାଇଛନ୍ତ
Assamese - Ahomia: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - কামৰ কাৰণে বা অন্য কাৰণত পৰিয়াল/শিশুতো বেলেগ ঠাইলৈ স্থানান্তৰ হল

Question Name: Reason for not in school - primary reason
Choice Text: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic
Kannada: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic  - ಒಡಹುಟ್ಟಿದವರನ್ನು ನೋಡಿಕೊಳ್ಳಲು/ಮನೆಯ ಕೆಲಸಗಳಲ್ಲಿ ಸಹಾಯ ಮಾಡಲು
Hindi: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic  - छोटे भाई-बहनों की देखभाल करना होती/घरेलू कामकाज में हाथ बँटाना होता है
Tamil: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic  - வீட்டில் உடன்பிறந்தவர்களை கவனித்துக்கொள்ள/ வீட்டு வேலைகளை கவனிக்க
Telugu: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic -  ఇంటిలో చిన్న పిల్లల సంరక్షణ భాధ్యత కొరకు / ఇంటి పనులు చేయుట కొరకు
Odiya: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic - ଭାଇଭଉଣୀଙ୍କ ଯତ୍ନ ନେବା ଜରୁରୀ/ ଦୈନନ୍ଦିନ ଘରୋଇ କାର୍ଯ୍ୟ କରିବା ଦରକାର
Assamese - Ahomia: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic - ভাই- ভ্নী সকলক চোৱাচিতা কৰিব লাগে

Question Name: Reason for not in school - primary reason
Choice Text: Parents perceive education as not useful
Kannada: Parents perceive education as not useful - ಪೋಷಕರು ಶಿಕ್ಷಣದಿಂದ ಏನೂ ಪ್ರಯೋಜನ ಇಲ್ಲ ಎಂದು ಪರಿಗಣಿಸಲು
Hindi: Parents perceive education as not useful - मातापिता को शिक्षा उपयोगी नहीं लगती
Tamil: Parents perceive education as not useful - படிப்பு பயனற்றது என்ற பெற்றோரின் பார்வை
Telugu: Parents perceive education as not useful -  విద్య వల్ల ఉపయోగము లేదని తల్లి దండ్రులు భావించడం
Odiya: Parents perceive education as not useful - ଶିକ୍ଷାର ଆବଶ୍ୟକତା ନାହିଁ ବୋଲି ପିତାମାତା ବୁଝାଇ ଦେଇଛନ୍ତି
Assamese - Ahomia: Parents perceive education as not useful - অভিভাবকে শিক্ষাক প্ৰয়োজনিয় বুলি নাভাবে

Question Name: Reason for not in school - primary reason
Kannada: Child not interested in education  - ಮಗುವಿಗೆ ಶಿಕ್ಷಣದಲ್ಲ್ಲಿ ಆಸಕ್ತಿ ಇಲ್ಲದಿರುವುದು
Hindi: Child not interested in education  - बच्चे की शिक्षा में रुचि नहीं है
Tamil: Child not interested in education  - படிப்பில் ஆர்வமின்மை
Telugu: Child not interested in education -  పిల్లలు (బాలుడు/బాలిక) చదువు పట్ల శ్రధ్ధచూపక పోవడం
Bangla: Child not interested in education - শিশুটি অনুতপ্ত হয় না
Odiya: Child not interested in education - ଶିଶୁ ଶିକ୍ଷା ପ୍ରତି ଆଗ୍ରହ ନାହିଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: Child not interested in education - শিশুটি শিক্ষাৰ প্ৰতি আগ্ৰহী নহয়

Question Name: Reason for not in school - primary reason
Reason for not in school - primary reason
Reason for not in school - primary reason
Kannada: Teaching in school not satisfactory - ಶಾಲೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ಪಾಠ ಮಾಡುವುದು ತೃಪ್ತಿಕರವಾಗಿಲ
Hindi: Teaching in school not satisfactory -  - स्कूल में पढ़ाई संतोषजनक नहीं है
Tamil: Teaching in school not satisfactory - பாடம் நடத்துவது திருப்பதியாக இல்லை
Telugu: Teaching in school not satisfactory -  పాఠశాలలో చదువు సంతృప్తికరంగా లేకపోవడం
Bangla: Teaching in school not good - স্কুলের পড়া ভাল না
Odiya: Teaching in school not good - ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟରେ ଶିକ୍ଷା ସନ୍ତୋଷଜନକ ନୁହେଁ

Question Name: Reason for not in school - primary reason
Choice Text: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory
Kannada: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - ಶಾಲೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ವ್ಯವಸ್ಥೆ ಸಮರ್ಪಕವಾಗಿಲ್ಲ/ತೃಪ್ತಿಕರವಾಗಿಲ
Hindi: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - स्कूल में सुविधाएं पर्याप्त/संतोषजनक नहीं हैं
Tamil: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - பள்ளியில் இருக்கும் வசதிகள் போதுமானதாக /திருப்தியாக இல்லை
Telugu: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory -  పాఠశాలలో వసతులు సరిగా లేకపోవడం / సంతృప్తి కరంగా లేక పోవడం
Odiya: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟରେ ଦିଆଯାଉଥିବା ଶିକ୍ଷା ପର୍ଯ୍ୟାପ୍ତ/ ସନ୍ତୋଷଜନକ ନୁହେଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - স্কুলত পৰ্য্যাপ্ত সা-সুবিধা নাই/ সন্তোশজনক নহয়

Question Name: Reason for not in school - primary reason
Choice Text: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient
Kannada: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient - ಶಾಲೆಯು ದೂರ ಇದೆ/ಶಾಲೆಗೆ ಪ್ರಯಾಣಿಸಲು ಅನುಕೂಲಕರವಾಗಿಲ್
Hindi: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient - स्कूल बहुत दूर स्थित है/स्कूल जाना-आना सुविधाजनक नहीं है
Tamil: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient - பள்ளி தொலைவில் உள்ளது/பள்ளிக்கு சென்று வருவது கடினம்
Telugu: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient -  పాఠశాల చాలా దూరముగా ఉండటం / పాఠశాలకు వెళ్ళుటకు సరియైన ప్రయాణ వసతి లేకపోవడం
Odiya: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient - ଦୂରରେ ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟ ରହିଛି/ ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟକୁ ଯିବା ସୁବିଧାଜନକ ନୁହେଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient - স্কুল বহু দুৰত

Question Name: Reason for not in school - primary reason
Choice Text: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe
Kannada: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - ಶಾಲೆ ಅಸುರಕ್ಷಿತ/ಶಾಲೆಗೆ ಪ್ರಯಾಣಿಸಲು ಅಸುರಕ್ಷಿತ
Hindi: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - स्कूल असुरक्षित/ स्कूल जाना-आना असुरक्षित है
Tamil: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - பள்ளி பாதுகாப்பாக இல்லை/பள்ளிக்கு செல்லும் வழி பாதுகாப்பாக இல்லை
Telugu: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe -  పాఠశాల సురక్షితం కాకపోవడం / పాఠశాలకు ప్రయాణం అసురక్షితం కావడం
Odiya: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - ଅସୁରକ୍ଷିତ ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟ/ ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟକୁ ଯିବା ଅସୁରକ୍ଷିତ
Assamese - Ahomia: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - যাতায়ত সুৰক্ষিত নহয়

Question Name: Reason for not in school - primary reason
Choice Text: Higher level schools are not available close to the village
Kannada: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - ಹಿರಿಯ ದರ್ಜೆಯ ಶಾಲೆಗಳು ಗ್ರಾಮದ ಸಮೀಪವಿಲ್
Hindi: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - उच्चतर स्तरीय स्कूल गाँव के नजदीक उपलब्ध नहीं हैं
Tamil: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - உயர், மேல்நிலை பள்ளிகள் கிராமத்திற்கு அருகில் இல்லை
Telugu: Higher level schools are not available close to the village -   ఉన్నత పాఠశాలలు గ్రామానికి దగ్గరలో లేక పోవడం
Odiya: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - ଉଚ୍ଚ ଶ୍ରେଣୀ ପାଇଁ ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟ ଗ୍ରାମ ନିକଟରେ ନାହିଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - উচ্চমানদন্দৰ স্কুল ওচৰত নাই

Question Name: Reason for not in school - primary reason
Choice Text: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM
Kannada: MDM (Mid Day Meal) not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM not good - ಎಮ್.ಡಿ.ಎಮ್  (Mid day meal) -  ಮಧ್ಯಾಹ್ನದ ಬಿಸಿ ಊಟ ದೊರಕುತ್ತಿಲ್ಲ ಅಥವಾ ನಿಯಮಿತವಾಗಿ ಸಿಗುತ್ತಿಲ್ಲ/ಎಮ್.ಡಿ.ಎಮ್. ಗುಣಮಟ್ಟ ಚೆನ್ನಾಗಿಲ್ಲ
Hindi: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM - मध्याह्न भोजन उपलब्ध नहीं है या नियमित उपलब्धता नहीं है/ मध्याह्न भोजन की   गुणवत्ता अच्छी नहीं है
Tamil: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM - மதிய உணவு வழங்கப்படவில்லை, தொடர்ந்து வழங்கப்படவில்லை/ உணவு தரமானதாக இல்லை
Telugu: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM -  మధ్యాహ్న భోజనం లేక పోవడం లేదా సక్రమముగా లేక పోవడం / మధ్యాహ్న భోజనం యొక్క నాణ్యత సరిగా లేకపోవడం

Kannada: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste - ಶಿಕ್ಷಕರಿಂದ ತಾರತಮ್ಯತೆ/ಉನ್ನತ ಜಾತಿಯ ಶಿಕ್ಷಕರಿಂದ ಅಸಭ್ಯ ವರ್ತನೆ

Hindi: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM - मध्याह्न भोजन उपलब्ध नहीं है या नियमित उपलब्धता नहीं है/ मध्याह्न भोजन की   गुणवत्ता अच्छी नहीं है
Tamil: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM - மதிய உணவு வழங்கப்படவில்லை, தொடர்ந்து வழங்கப்படவில்லை/ உணவு தரமானதாக இல்லை
Telugu: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM -  మధ్యాహ్న భోజనం లేక పోవడం లేదా సక్రమముగా లేక పోవడం / మధ్యాహ్న భోజనం యొక్క నాణ్యత సరిగా లేకపోవడం

Choice Text: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste
Kannada: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste - ಶಿಕ್ಷಕರಿಂದ ತಾರತಮ್ಯತೆ/ಉನ್ನತ ಜಾತಿಯ ಶಿಕ್ಷಕರಿಂದ ಅಸಭ್ಯ ವರ್ತನೆ
Hindi: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste - ऊँची जाति के शिक्षकों द्वारा भेदभाव/दुर्व्यवहार किया जाता है
Tamil: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste - ஆசிரியர்கள்  பாகுபாடுகாட்டுதல்/ உயர் சாதி ஆசிரியர்கள் மாணவர்களிடம் தவறாக நடத்தல்
Telugu: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste -  ఉపాధ్యాయులు వివక్ష చూపడం / అగ్రవర్ణానికి చెందిన ఉపాధ్యాయుడు వర్ణ వివక్షత చూపడం

Choice Text: Discrimination by other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste
Kannada: Discrimination by other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste - ಇತರ ಮಕ್ಕಳಿಂದ ತಾರತಮ್ಯತೆ/ಉನ್ನತ ಜಾತಿಯ ಇತರ ಮಕ್ಕಳಿಂದ ಅಸಭ್ಯ ವರ್ತನೆ
Hindi: Discrimination by other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste - ऊँची जाति के अन्य छात्रों द्वारा भेदभाव/दुर्व्यवहार किया जाता है
Tamil: Discrimination by other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste - பிற மாணவர்களால் பாகுபடுகாட்டப்படுதல்/ பிற உயர் சாதி மாணவர்கள் தவறாக நடத்தல்
Telugu: Discrimination by other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste -  పాఠశాలలోని ఇతర పిల్లలు వివక్ష చూపడం / అగ్రవర్ణాలకు చెందిన పిల్లలు అనుచితముగా ప్రవర్తించడము

Choice Text: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation
Kannada: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation -  ಕೆಲಸದಲ್ಲಿ ಕುಟುಂಬಕ್ಕೆ ಸಹಾಯ ಮಾಡಬೇಕಿದೆ/ಕೌಟುಂಬಿಕ ಉದ್ಯೋಗ
Hindi: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - काम में परिवार की मदद की आवश्यकता/घरेलू व्यवसाय
Tamil: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - குடும்பத்தினருக்கு வேலையில் உதவுதல்/வீட்டு வேலை
Telugu: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation -  కుటుంబమునకు సహాయపడటానికి (పనులకు) / కుటుంబ వృత్తికి తోడ్పడటానికి
Bangla: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - পরিবারের সাহায্য প্রয়োজন

Choice Text: Child need to work to earn money (labour work)
Kannada: Child need to work to earn money (labour work)ಹಣ ಸಂಪಾದಿಸಲು ಮಗುವು ಕೆಲಸ ಮಾಡಬೇಕಿರುವ ಅವಶ್ಯಕತೆ (ಕೂಲಿ ಕೆಲಸ)
Hindi: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - पैसा कमाने के लिये बच्चे को काम करना पड़ता है (बाल श्रम)
Tamil: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - குழந்தைத் தொழிலாளர்
Telugu: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) -  పిల్లలు కుటుంబ సంపాదన కొరకు పనిచేయాలి (కూలీ ప నులకు)
Bangla: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - শিশুকে অর্থ উপার্জন করতে হবে
Assamese - Ahomia: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - উপাৰ্জন কৰিবলৈ কাম কৰিব লাগে

Choice Text: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other
Kannada: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - ಕೆಲಸಕ್ಕಾಗಿ ಅಥವಾ ಬೇರೆ ಉದ್ದೇಶಕ್ಕಾಗಿ ಕುಟುಂಬ/ಮಗುವು ಬೇರೆಡೆಗೆ ವಲಸೆ ಹೋಗಿರುವುದು
Hindi: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - परिवार/बच्चे को काम के लिये दूसरी जगह विस्थापित होना पड़ा या किसी अन्य कारण से
Tamil: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - குடும்பம்/குழந்தை வேலைக்காக அல்லது வேறு நோக்கத்திற்காக இடம்பெயர்ந்து சென்றது
Telugu: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other -  కుటుంబము / పిల్లలు  పనులు/సంపాదన/ఇతర కారణము తో ఇతర ప్రాంతములకు వలస వెళ్ళినారు

Choice Text: Parents perceive education as not useful
Kannada: Parents perceive education as not useful - ಪೋಷಕರು ಶಿಕ್ಷಣದಿಂದ ಏನೂ ಪ್ರಯೋಜನ ಇಲ್ಲ ಎಂದು ಪರಿಗಣಿಸಲು
Hindi: Parents perceive education as not useful - मातापिता को शिक्षा उपयोगी नहीं लगती
Tamil: Parents perceive education as not useful - படிப்பு பயனற்றது என்ற பெற்றோரின் பார்வை
Telugu: Parents perceive education as not useful -  విద్య వల్ల ఉపయోగము లేదని తల్లి దండ్రులు భావించడం

Kannada: Child not interested in education - ಮಗುವಿಗೆ ಶಿಕ್ಷಣದಲ್ಲ್ಲಿ ಆಸಕ್ತಿ ಇಲ್ಲದಿರುವುದು
Hindi: Child not interested in education - बच्चे की शिक्षा में रुचि नहीं है
Tamil: Child not interested in education - படிப்பில் ஆர்வமின்மை
Telugu: Child not interested in education -  పిల్లలు (బాలుడు/బాలిక) చదువు పట్ల శ్రధ్ధచూపక పోవడం
Bangla: Child not interested in education - শিশুটি অনুতপ্ত হয় না
Assamese - Ahomia: Child not interested in education - শিশুটি শিক্ষাৰ প্ৰতি আগ্ৰহী নহয়

Kannada: Teaching in school not satisfactory -  ಶಾಲೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ಪಾಠ ಮಾಡುವುದು ತೃಪ್ತಿಕರವಾಗಿಲ
Hindi: Teaching in school not satisfactory - स्कूल में पढ़ाई संतोषजनक नहीं है
Tamil: Teaching in school not satisfactory - பாடம் நடத்துவது திருப்பதியாக இல்லை
Telugu: Teaching in school not satisfactory -  పాఠశాలలో చదువు సంతృప్తికరంగా లేకపోవడం

Choice Text: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory
Kannada: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - ಶಾಲೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ವ್ಯವಸ್ಥೆ ಸಮರ್ಪಕವಾಗಿಲ್ಲ/ತೃಪ್ತಿಕರವಾಗಿಲ
Hindi: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory स्कूल में सुविधाएं पर्याप्त/संतोषजनक नहीं हैं
Tamil: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - பள்ளியில் இருக்கும் வசதிகள் போதுமானதாக /திருப்தியாக இல்லை
Telugu: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory -  పాఠశాలలో వసతులు సరిగా లేకపోవడం / సంతృప్తి కరంగా లేక పోవడం

Choice Text: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient
Kannada: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient - ಶಾಲೆಯು ದೂರ ಇದೆ/ಶಾಲೆಗೆ ಪ್ರಯಾಣಿಸಲು ಅನುಕೂಲಕರವಾಗಿಲ್
Hindi: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient - स्कूल बहुत दूर स्थित है/स्कूल जाना-आना सुविधाजनक नहीं है
Tamil: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient - பள்ளி தொலைவில் உள்ளது/பள்ளிக்கு சென்று வருவது கடினம்
Telugu: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient -  పాఠశాల చాలా దూరముగా ఉండటం / పాఠశాలకు వెళ్ళుటకు సరియైన ప్రయాణ వసతి లేకపోవడం

Choice Text: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe
Kannada: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - ಶಾಲೆ ಅಸುರಕ್ಷಿತ/ಶಾಲೆಗೆ ಪ್ರಯಾಣಿಸಲು ಅಸುರಕ್ಷಿತ
Hindi: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - स्कूल असुरक्षित/ स्कूल जाना-आना असुरक्षित है
Tamil: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - பள்ளி பாதுகாப்பாக இல்லை/பள்ளிக்கு செல்லும் வழி பாதுகாப்பாக இல்லை
Telugu: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe -  పాఠశాల సురక్షితం కాకపోవడం / పాఠశాలకు ప్రయాణం అసురక్షితం కావడం

Choice Text: Higher level schools are not available close to the village
Kannada: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - ಹಿರಿಯ ದರ್ಜೆಯ ಶಾಲೆಗಳು ಗ್ರಾಮದ ಸಮೀಪವಿಲ್
Hindi: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - उच्चतर स्तरीय स्कूल गाँव के नजदीक उपलब्ध नहीं हैं
Tamil: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - உயர், மேல்நிலை பள்ளிகள் கிராமத்திற்கு அருகில் இல்லை
Telugu: Higher level schools are not available close to the village -  ఉన్నత పాఠశాలలు గ్రామానికి దగ్గరలో లేక పోవడం

Hindi: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - पैसा कमाने के लिये बच्चे को काम करना पड़ता है (बाल श्रम)
Tamil: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - குழந்தைத் தொழிலாளர்
Telugu: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) -  పిల్లలు కుటుంబ సంపాదన కొరకు పనిచేయాలి (కూలీ ప నులకు)
Bangla: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - শিশুকে অর্থ উপার্জন করতে হবে
Odiya: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - ଅର୍ଥ ଉପାର୍ଜନ ପାଇଁ ଶିଶୁ ଯଦି କାମ କରିବାକୁ ଚାହୁଁଛି
Assamese - Ahomia: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - উপাৰ্জন কৰিবলৈ কাম কৰিব লাগে

Question Name: Secondary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other
Kannada: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - ಕೆಲಸಕ್ಕಾಗಿ ಅಥವಾ ಬೇರೆ ಉದ್ದೇಶಕ್ಕಾಗಿ ಕುಟುಂಬ/ಮಗುವು ಬೇರೆಡೆಗೆ ವಲಸೆ ಹೋಗಿರುವುದು
Hindi: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - परिवार/बच्चे को काम के लिये दूसरी जगह विस्थापित होना पड़ा या किसी अन्य कारण से
Tamil: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - குடும்பம்/குழந்தை வேலைக்காக அல்லது வேறு நோக்கத்திற்காக இடம்பெயர்ந்து சென்றது
Telugu: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other -  కుటుంబము / పిల్లలు  పనులు/సంపాదన/ఇతర కారణము తో ఇతర ప్రాంతములకు వలస వెళ్ళినారు
Odiya: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - ପରିବାର/ ଶିଶୁ କାମ ପାଇଁ କିମ୍ବା ଅନ୍ୟ କୌଣସି କାରଣ ପାଇଁ ଅନ୍ୟ ସ୍ଥାନକୁ ସ୍ଥାନାନ୍ତର ହୋଇ ଯାଇଛନ୍ତ
Assamese - Ahomia: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - কামৰ কাৰণে বা অন্য কাৰণত পৰিয়াল/শিশুতো বেলেগ ঠাইলৈ স্থানান্তৰ হল

Question Name: Secondary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic
Kannada: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic  - ಒಡಹುಟ್ಟಿದವರನ್ನು ನೋಡಿಕೊಳ್ಳಲು/ಮನೆಯ ಕೆಲಸಗಳಲ್ಲಿ ಸಹಾಯ ಮಾಡಲು
Hindi: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic -  छोटे भाई-बहनों की देखभाल करना होती/घरेलू कामकाज में हाथ बँटाना होता है
Tamil: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic - வீட்டில் உடன்பிறந்தவர்களை கவனித்துக்கொள்ள/ வீட்டு வேலைகளை கவனிக்க
Telugu: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic -  ఇంటిలో చిన్న పిల్లల సంరక్షణ భాధ్యత కొరకు / ఇంటి పనులు చేయుట కొరకు
Odiya: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic - ଭାଇଭଉଣୀଙ୍କ ଯତ୍ନ ନେବା ଜରୁରୀ/ ଦୈନନ୍ଦିନ ଘରୋଇ କାର୍ଯ୍ୟ କରିବା ଦରକାର
Assamese - Ahomia: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic - ভাই- ভ্নী সকলক চোৱাচিতা কৰিব লাগে

Question Name: Secondary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Parents perceive education as not useful
Kannada: Parents perceive education as not useful - ಪೋಷಕರು ಶಿಕ್ಷಣದಿಂದ ಏನೂ ಪ್ರಯೋಜನ ಇಲ್ಲ ಎಂದು ಪರಿಗಣಿಸಲು
Hindi: Parents perceive education as not useful - मातापिता को शिक्षा उपयोगी नहीं लगती
Tamil: Parents perceive education as not useful - படிப்பு பயனற்றது என்ற பெற்றோரின் பார்வை
Telugu: Parents perceive education as not useful -  విద్య వల్ల ఉపయోగము లేదని తల్లి దండ్రులు భావించడం
Odiya: Parents perceive education as not useful - ଶିକ୍ଷାର ଆବଶ୍ୟକତା ନାହିଁ ବୋଲି ପିତାମାତା ବୁଝାଇ ଦେଇଛନ୍ତି
Assamese - Ahomia: Parents perceive education as not useful - অভিভাবকে শিক্ষাক প্ৰয়োজনিয় বুলি নাভাবে

Question Name: Secondary reason for not in school
Kannada: Child not interested in education  - ಮಗುವಿಗೆ ಶಿಕ್ಷಣದಲ್ಲ್ಲಿ ಆಸಕ್ತಿ ಇಲ್ಲದಿರುವುದು
Hindi: Child not interested in education - बच्चे की शिक्षा में रुचि नहीं है
Tamil: Child not interested in education - படிப்பில் ஆர்வமின்மை
Telugu: Child not interested in education -  పిల్లలు (బాలుడు/బాలిక) చదువు పట్ల శ్రధ్ధచూపక పోవడం
Bangla: Child not interested in education - শিশুটি অনুতপ্ত হয় না
Odiya: Child not interested in education - ଶିଶୁ ଶିକ୍ଷା ପ୍ରତି ଆଗ୍ରହ ନାହିଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: Child not interested in education - শিশুটি শিক্ষাৰ প্ৰতি আগ্ৰহী নহয়

Question Name: Secondary reason for not in school
Secondary reason for not in school
Secondary reason for not in school
Kannada: Teaching in school not satisfactory - ಶಾಲೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ಪಾಠ ಮಾಡುವುದು ತೃಪ್ತಿಕರವಾಗಿಲ
Hindi: Teaching in school not satisfactory - स्कूल में पढ़ाई संतोषजनक नहीं है
Tamil: Teaching in school not satisfactory - பாடம் நடத்துவது திருப்பதியாக இல்லை
Telugu: Teaching in school not satisfactory -  పాఠశాలలో చదువు సంతృప్తికరంగా లేకపోవడం
Odiya: Teaching in school not satisfactory - ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟରେ ଶିକ୍ଷା ସନ୍ତୋଷଜନକ ନୁହେଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: Teaching in school not satisfactory - স্কূলৰ শিক্ষা সন্তোশজনক নহয়

Question Name: Secondary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory
Kannada: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - ಶಾಲೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ವ್ಯವಸ್ಥೆ ಸಮರ್ಪಕವಾಗಿಲ್ಲ/ತೃಪ್ತಿಕರವಾಗಿಲ
Hindi: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - स्कूल में सुविधाएं पर्याप्त/संतोषजनक नहीं हैं
Tamil: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - பள்ளியில் இருக்கும் வசதிகள் போதுமானதாக /திருப்தியாக இல்லை
Telugu: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory -  పాఠశాలలో వసతులు సరిగా లేకపోవడం / సంతృప్తి కరంగా లేక పోవడం
Odiya: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟରେ ଦିଆଯାଉଥିବା ଶିକ୍ଷା ପର୍ଯ୍ୟାପ୍ତ/ ସନ୍ତୋଷଜନକ ନୁହେଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - স্কুলত পৰ্য্যাপ্ত সা-সুবিধা নাই/ সন্তোশজনক নহয়

Question Name: Secondary reason for not in school
Choice Text: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe
Kannada: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - ಶಾಲೆ ಅಸುರಕ್ಷಿತ/ಶಾಲೆಗೆ ಪ್ರಯಾಣಿಸಲು ಅಸುರಕ್ಷಿತ
Hindi: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - स्कूल असुरक्षित/ स्कूल जाना-आना असुरक्षित है
Tamil: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - பள்ளி பாதுகாப்பாக இல்லை/பள்ளிக்கு செல்லும் வழி பாதுகாப்பாக இல்லை
Telugu: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe -  పాఠశాల సురక్షితం కాకపోవడం / పాఠశాలకు ప్రయాణం అసురక్షితం కావడం
Odiya: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - ଅସୁରକ୍ଷିତ ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟ/ ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟକୁ ଯିବା ଅସୁରକ୍ଷିତ
Assamese - Ahomia: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - যাতায়ত সুৰক্ষিত নহয়

Question Name: Secondary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Higher level schools are not available close to the village
Kannada: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - ಹಿರಿಯ ದರ್ಜೆಯ ಶಾಲೆಗಳು ಗ್ರಾಮದ ಸಮೀಪವಿಲ್
Hindi: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - उच्चतर स्तरीय स्कूल गाँव के नजदीक उपलब्ध नहीं हैं
Tamil: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - உயர், மேல்நிலை பள்ளிகள் கிராமத்திற்கு அருகில் இல்லை
Telugu: Higher level schools are not available close to the village -  ఉన్నత పాఠశాలలు గ్రామానికి దగ్గరలో లేక పోవడం
Odiya: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - ଉଚ୍ଚ ଶ୍ରେଣୀ ପାଇଁ ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟ ଗ୍ରାମ ନିକଟରେ ନାହିଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - উচ্চমানদন্দৰ স্কুল ওচৰত নাই

Question Name: Secondary reason for not in school
Choice Text: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM
Kannada: MDM (Mid Day Meal) not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM not good - ಎಮ್.ಡಿ.ಎಮ್  (Mid day meal) -  ಮಧ್ಯಾಹ್ನದ ಬಿಸಿ ಊಟ ದೊರಕುತ್ತಿಲ್ಲ ಅಥವಾ ನಿಯಮಿತವಾಗಿ ಸಿಗುತ್ತಿಲ್ಲ/ಎಮ್.ಡಿ.ಎಮ್. ಗುಣಮಟ್ಟ ಚೆನ್ನಾಗಿಲ್ಲ
Hindi: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM - मध्याह्न भोजन उपलब्ध नहीं है या नियमित उपलब्धता नहीं है/ मध्याह्न भोजन की   गुणवत्ता अच्छी नहीं है
Tamil: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM - மதிய உணவு வழங்கப்படவில்லை, தொடர்ந்து வழங்கப்படவில்லை/ உணவு தரமானதாக இல்லை
Telugu: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM -  మధ్యాహ్న భోజనం లేక పోవడం లేదా సక్రమముగా లేక పోవడం / మధ్యాహ్న భోజనం యొక్క నాణ్యత సరిగా లేకపోవడం
Odiya: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM - ମଧ୍ୟାହ୍ନ ଭୋଜନ ମିଳୁନାହିଁ କିମ୍ବା ଅନିୟମିତ ଭାବେ ମିଳୁଛି/ ମଧ୍ୟାହ୍ନ ଭୋଜନର ମାନ ଭଲ ନୁହେଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM - মধ্যহ্নভোজন (MDM) উপলব্ধ নহয়/ মানদন্দ উন্নত নহয়)

Question Name: Secondary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste
Kannada: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste - ಶಿಕ್ಷಕರಿಂದ ತಾರತಮ್ಯತೆ/ಉನ್ನತ ಜಾತಿಯ ಶಿಕ್ಷಕರಿಂದ ಅಸಭ್ಯ ವರ್ತನೆ
Hindi: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste - ऊँची जाति के शिक्षकों द्वारा भेदभाव/दुर्व्यवहार किया जाता है
Tamil: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste - ஆசிரியர்கள்  பாகுபாடுகாட்டுதல்/ உயர் சாதி ஆசிரியர்கள் மாணவர்களிடம் தவறாக நடத்தல்
Telugu: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste -  ఉపాధ్యాయులు వివక్ష చూపడం / అగ్రవర్ణానికి చెందిన ఉపాధ్యాయుడు వర్ణ వివక్షత చూపడం
Odiya: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste - ଶିକ୍ଷକଙ୍କ ଭେଦଭାବର ଶିକାର/ ଉଚ୍ଚ ଶ୍ରେଣୀର ଶିକ୍ଷକମାନଙ୍କ ଖରାପ ବ୍ୟବହାରର ଶିକାର
Assamese - Ahomia: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste - শিক্ষকৰ দ্বাৰা প্ৰতাৰিত/বেয়া ব্যবহাৰ

Question Name: Secondary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Discrimination by other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste
Kannada: Discrimination by other other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste  - ಇತರ ಮಕ್ಕಳಿಂದ ತಾರತಮ್ಯತೆ/ಉನ್ನತ ಜಾತಿಯ ಇತರ ಮಕ್ಕಳಿಂದ ಅಸಭ್ಯ ವರ್ತನೆ
Hindi: Discrimination by other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste -  ऊँची जाति के अन्य छात्रों द्वारा भेदभाव/दुर्व्यवहार किया जाता है
Tamil: Discrimination by other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste - பிற மாணவர்களால் பாகுபடுகாட்டப்படுதல்/ பிற உயர் சாதி மாணவர்கள் தவறாக நடத்தல்
Telugu: Discrimination by other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste -  పాఠశాలలోని ఇతర పిల్లలు వివక్ష చూపడం / అగ్రవర్ణాలకు చెందిన పిల్లలు అనుచితముగా ప్రవర్తించడము
Odiya: Discrimination by other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste - ଅନ୍ୟ ଛାତ୍ରଛାତ୍ରୀଙ୍କ ଭେଦଭାବର ଶିକାର/ ଉଚ୍ଚ ଶ୍ରେଣୀର ଛାତ୍ରଛାତ୍ରୀମାନଙ୍କ ଖରାପ ବ୍ୟବହାରର ଶିକାର
Assamese - Ahomia: Discrimination by other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste - সতিৰ্থ শিক্ষাৰ্থিৰ দ্বাৰা প্ৰতাৰিত/বেয়া ব্যবহাৰ

Question Name: Secondary reason for not in school
Secondary reason for not in school
Secondary reason for not in school
Tertiary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation
Kannada: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - ಕೆಲಸದಲ್ಲಿ ಕುಟುಂಬಕ್ಕೆ ಸಹಾಯ ಮಾಡಬೇಕಿದೆ/ಕೌಟುಂಬಿಕ ಉದ್ಯೋಗ
Hindi: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - काम में परिवार की मदद की आवश्यकता/घरेलू व्यवसाय
Tamil: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - குடும்பத்தினருக்கு வேலையில் உதவுதல்/வீட்டு வேலை
Telugu: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation -  కుటుంబమునకు సహాయపడటానికి (పనులకు) / కుటుంబ వృత్తికి తోడ్పడటానికి
Bangla: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - পরিবারের সাহায্য প্রয়োজন
Odiya: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - ପରିବାରକୁ କାମରେ ସହାଯ୍ୟ କରିବା ଦରକାର/ ପରିବାରର ପେଶା
Assamese - Ahomia: Need to help family in work/ Household occupation - ঘৰত কাম কৰিব লাগে/ঘৰুৱা বৃত্তিত সহায়ৰ কাৰণে

Question Name: Tertiary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Child need to work to earn money
Kannada: Child need to work to earn money (labour work) - ಹಣ ಸಂಪಾದಿಸಲು ಮಗುವು ಕೆಲಸ ಮಾಡಬೇಕಿರುವ ಅವಶ್ಯಕತೆ (ಕೂಲಿ ಕೆಲಸ)
Hindi: Child need to work to earn money
Tamil: Child need to work to earn money - पैसा कमाने के लिये बच्चे को काम करना पड़ता है (बाल श्रम)  - குழந்தைத் தொழிலாளர்
Telugu: Child need to work to earn money -  పిల్లలు కుటుంబ సంపాదన కొరకు పనిచేయాలి (కూలీ ప నులకు)
Bangla: Child need to work to earn money - শিশুকে অর্থ উপার্জন করতে হবে
Odiya: Child need to work to earn money - ଅର୍ଥ ଉପାର୍ଜନ ପାଇଁ ଶିଶୁ ଯଦି କାମ କରିବାକୁ ଚାହୁଁଛି
Assamese - Ahomia: Child need to work to earn money - উপাৰ্জন কৰিবলৈ কাম কৰিব লাগে

Question Name: Tertiary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other
Kannada: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - ಕೆಲಸಕ್ಕಾಗಿ ಅಥವಾ ಬೇರೆ ಉದ್ದೇಶಕ್ಕಾಗಿ ಕುಟುಂಬ/ಮಗುವು ಬೇರೆಡೆಗೆ ವಲಸೆ ಹೋಗಿರುವುದು
Hindi: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - परिवार/बच्चे को काम के लिये दूसरी जगह विस्थापित होना पड़ा या किसी अन्य कारण से
Tamil: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - குடும்பம்/குழந்தை வேலைக்காக அல்லது வேறு நோக்கத்திற்காக இடம்பெயர்ந்து சென்றது
Telugu: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other -  కుటుంబము / పిల్లలు  పనులు/సంపాదన/ఇతర కారణము తో ఇతర ప్రాంతములకు వలస వెళ్ళినారు
Odiya: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - ପରିବାର/ ଶିଶୁ କାମ ପାଇଁ କିମ୍ବା ଅନ୍ୟ କୌଣସି କାରଣ ପାଇଁ ଅନ୍ୟ ସ୍ଥାନକୁ ସ୍ଥାନାନ୍ତର ହୋଇ ଯାଇଛନ୍ତ
Assamese - Ahomia: Family/ child migrated to other place for work or any other - কামৰ কাৰণে বা অন্য কাৰণত পৰিয়াল/শিশুতো বেলেগ ঠাইলৈ স্থানান্তৰ হল

Question Name: Tertiary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic
Kannada: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic  - ಒಡಹುಟ್ಟಿದವರನ್ನು ನೋಡಿಕೊಳ್ಳಲು/ಮನೆಯ ಕೆಲಸಗಳಲ್ಲಿ ಸಹಾಯ ಮಾಡಲು
Hindi: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic - छोटे भाई-बहनों की देखभाल करना होती/घरेलू कामकाज में हाथ बँटाना होता है
Tamil: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic - வீட்டில் உடன்பிறந்தவர்களை கவனித்துக்கொள்ள/ வீட்டு வேலைகளை கவனிக்க
Telugu: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic -  ఇంటిలో చిన్న పిల్లల సంరక్షణ భాధ్యత కొరకు / ఇంటి పనులు చేయుట కొరకు
Odiya: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic - ଭାଇଭଉଣୀଙ୍କ ଯତ୍ନ ନେବା ଜରୁରୀ/ ଦୈନନ୍ଦିନ ଘରୋଇ କାର୍ଯ୍ୟ କରିବା ଦରକାର
Assamese - Ahomia: Need to take care of siblings/ need to take care of domestic - ভাই- ভ্নী সকলক চোৱাচিতা কৰিব লাগে

Question Name: Tertiary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Parents perceive education as not useful
Kannada: Parents perceive education as not useful - ಪೋಷಕರು ಶಿಕ್ಷಣದಿಂದ ಏನೂ ಪ್ರಯೋಜನ ಇಲ್ಲ ಎಂದು ಪರಿಗಣಿಸಲು
Hindi: Parents perceive education as not useful - मातापिता को शिक्षा उपयोगी नहीं लगती
Tamil: Parents perceive education as not useful - படிப்பு பயனற்றது என்ற பெற்றோரின் பார்வை
Telugu: Parents perceive education as not useful -  విద్య వల్ల ఉపయోగము లేదని తల్లి దండ్రులు భావించడం
Odiya: Parents perceive education as not useful - ଶିକ୍ଷାର ଆବଶ୍ୟକତା ନାହିଁ ବୋଲି ପିତାମାତା ବୁଝାଇ ଦେଇଛନ୍ତି
Assamese - Ahomia: Parents perceive education as not useful - অভিভাবকে শিক্ষাক প্ৰয়োজনিয় বুলি নাভাবে

Question Name: Tertiary reason for not in school
Kannada: Child not interested in education  - ಮಗುವಿಗೆ ಶಿಕ್ಷಣದಲ್ಲ್ಲಿ ಆಸಕ್ತಿ ಇಲ್ಲದಿರುವುದು
Hindi: Child not interested in education - बच्चे की शिक्षा में रुचि नहीं है
Tamil: Child not interested in education - படிப்பில் ஆர்வமின்மை
Telugu: Child not interested in education -  పిల్లలు (బాలుడు/బాలిక) చదువు పట్ల శ్రధ్ధచూపక పోవడం
Bangla: Child not interested in education - শিশুটি অনুতপ্ত হয় না
Odiya: Child not interested in education - ଶିଶୁ ଶିକ୍ଷା ପ୍ରତି ଆଗ୍ରହ ନାହିଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: Child not interested in education - শিশুটি শিক্ষাৰ প্ৰতি আগ্ৰহী নহয়

Question Name: Tertiary reason for not in school
Tertiary reason for not in school
Tertiary reason for not in school
Kannada: Teaching in school not satisfactory - ಶಾಲೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ಪಾಠ ಮಾಡುವುದು ತೃಪ್ತಿಕರವಾಗಿಲ
Hindi: Teaching in school not satisfactory -  स्कूल में पढ़ाई संतोषजनक नहीं है
Tamil: Teaching in school not satisfactory - பாடம் நடத்துவது திருப்பதியாக இல்லை
Telugu: Teaching in school not satisfactory -  పాఠశాలలో చదువు సంతృప్తికరంగా లేకపోవడం
Odiya: Teaching in school not satisfactory - ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟରେ ଶିକ୍ଷା ସନ୍ତୋଷଜନକ ନୁହେଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: Teaching in school not satisfactory - স্কূলৰ শিক্ষা সন্তোশজনক নহয়

Question Name: Tertiary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory
Kannada: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - ಶಾಲೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ವ್ಯವಸ್ಥೆ ಸಮರ್ಪಕವಾಗಿಲ್ಲ/ತೃಪ್ತಿಕರವಾಗಿಲ
Hindi: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - स्कूल में सुविधाएं पर्याप्त/संतोषजनक नहीं हैं
Tamil: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - பள்ளியில் இருக்கும் வசதிகள் போதுமானதாக /திருப்தியாக இல்லை
Telugu: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory -  పాఠశాలలో వసతులు సరిగా లేకపోవడం / సంతృప్తి కరంగా లేక పోవడం
Odiya: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟରେ ଦିଆଯାଉଥିବା ଶିକ୍ଷା ପର୍ଯ୍ୟାପ୍ତ/ ସନ୍ତୋଷଜନକ ନୁହେଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: Facilities in school are not adequate/ satisfactory - স্কুলত পৰ্য্যাপ্ত সা-সুবিধা নাই/ সন্তোশজনক নহয়

Question Name: Tertiary reason for not in school
Choice Text: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient
Kannada: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient - ಶಾಲೆಯು ದೂರ ಇದೆ/ಶಾಲೆಗೆ ಪ್ರಯಾಣಿಸಲು ಅನುಕೂಲಕರವಾಗಿಲ್
Hindi: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient - स्कूल बहुत दूर स्थित है/स्कूल जाना-आना सुविधाजनक नहीं है
Tamil: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient - பள்ளி தொலைவில் உள்ளது/பள்ளிக்கு சென்று வருவது கடினம்
Telugu: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient -  పాఠశాల చాలా దూరముగా ఉండటం / పాఠశాలకు వెళ్ళుటకు సరియైన ప్రయాణ వసతి లేకపోవడం
Odiya: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient - ଦୂରରେ ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟ ରହିଛି/ ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟକୁ ଯିବା ସୁବିଧାଜନକ ନୁହେଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: School at a long distance/ Travel to school not convenient - স্কুল বহু দুৰত

Question Name: Tertiary reason for not in school
Choice Text: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe
Kannada: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - ಶಾಲೆ ಅಸುರಕ್ಷಿತ/ಶಾಲೆಗೆ ಪ್ರಯಾಣಿಸಲು ಅಸುರಕ್ಷಿತ
Hindi: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - स्कूल असुरक्षित/ स्कूल जाना-आना असुरक्षित है
Tamil: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - பள்ளி பாதுகாப்பாக இல்லை/பள்ளிக்கு செல்லும் வழி பாதுகாப்பாக இல்லை
Telugu: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe -  పాఠశాల సురక్షితం కాకపోవడం / పాఠశాలకు ప్రయాణం అసురక్షితం కావడం
Odiya: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - ଅସୁରକ୍ଷିତ ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟ/ ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟକୁ ଯିବା ଅସୁରକ୍ଷିତ
Assamese - Ahomia: School unsafe/ travel to school unsafe - যাতায়ত সুৰক্ষিত নহয়

Question Name: Tertiary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Higher level schools are not available close to the village
Kannada: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - ಹಿರಿಯ ದರ್ಜೆಯ ಶಾಲೆಗಳು ಗ್ರಾಮದ ಸಮೀಪವಿಲ್
Hindi: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - उच्चतर स्तरीय स्कूल गाँव के नजदीक उपलब्ध नहीं हैं
Tamil: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - உயர், மேல்நிலை பள்ளிகள் கிராமத்திற்கு அருகில் இல்லை
Telugu: Higher level schools are not available close to the village -  ఉన్నత పాఠశాలలు గ్రామానికి దగ్గరలో లేక పోవడం
Odiya: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - ଉଚ୍ଚ ଶ୍ରେଣୀ ପାଇଁ ବିଦ୍ୟାଳୟ ଗ୍ରାମ ନିକଟରେ ନାହିଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: Higher level schools are not available close to the village - উচ্চমানদন্দৰ স্কুল ওচৰত নাই

Question Name: Tertiary reason for not in school
Choice Text: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM
Kannada: MDM (Mid Day Meal) not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM not good - ಎಮ್.ಡಿ.ಎಮ್  (Mid day meal) -  ಮಧ್ಯಾಹ್ನದ ಬಿಸಿ ಊಟ ದೊರಕುತ್ತಿಲ್ಲ ಅಥವಾ ನಿಯಮಿತವಾಗಿ ಸಿಗುತ್ತಿಲ್ಲ/ಎಮ್.ಡಿ.ಎಮ್. ಗುಣಮಟ್ಟ ಚೆನ್ನಾಗಿಲ್ಲ
Hindi: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM - मध्याह्न भोजन उपलब्ध नहीं है या नियमित उपलब्धता नहीं है/ मध्याह्न भोजन की   गुणवत्ता अच्छी नहीं है
Tamil: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM - மதிய உணவு வழங்கப்படவில்லை, தொடர்ந்து வழங்கப்படவில்லை/ உணவு தரமானதாக இல்லை
Telugu: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM -  మధ్యాహ్న భోజనం లేక పోవడం లేదా సక్రమముగా లేక పోవడం / మధ్యాహ్న భోజనం యొక్క నాణ్యత సరిగా లేకపోవడం
Odiya: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM - ମଧ୍ୟାହ୍ନ ଭୋଜନ ମିଳୁନାହିଁ କିମ୍ବା ଅନିୟମିତ ଭାବେ ମିଳୁଛି/ ମଧ୍ୟାହ୍ନ ଭୋଜନର ମାନ ଭଲ ନୁହେଁ
Assamese - Ahomia: MDM not available or not available regularly/ Quality of MDM - মধ্যহ্নভোজন (MDM) উপলব্ধ নহয়/ মানদন্দ উন্নত নহয়)

Question Name: Tertiary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste
Kannada: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste - ಶಿಕ್ಷಕರಿಂದ ತಾರತಮ್ಯತೆ/ಉನ್ನತ ಜಾತಿಯ ಶಿಕ್ಷಕರಿಂದ ಅಸಭ್ಯ ವರ್ತನೆ
Hindi: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste - ऊँची जाति के शिक्षकों द्वारा भेदभाव/दुर्व्यवहार किया जाता है
Tamil: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste - ஆசிரியர்கள்  பாகுபாடுகாட்டுதல்/ உயர் சாதி ஆசிரியர்கள் மாணவர்களிடம் தவறாக நடத்தல்
Telugu: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste -  ఉపాధ్యాయులు వివక్ష చూపడం / అగ్రవర్ణానికి చెందిన ఉపాధ్యాయుడు వర్ణ వివక్షత చూపడం
Odiya: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste - ଶିକ୍ଷକଙ୍କ ଭେଦଭାବର ଶିକାର/ ଉଚ୍ଚ ଶ୍ରେଣୀର ଶିକ୍ଷକମାନଙ୍କ ଖରାପ ବ୍ୟବହାରର ଶିକାର
Assamese - Ahomia: Discrimination by teacher/ Misbehaviour by teacher from higher caste - শিক্ষকৰ দ্বাৰা প্ৰতাৰিত/বেয়া ব্যবহাৰ

Question Name: Tertiary reason for not in school
Choice Text: Discrimination by other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste
Kannada: Discrimination by other other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste  - ಇತರ ಮಕ್ಕಳಿಂದ ತಾರತಮ್ಯತೆ/ಉನ್ನತ ಜಾತಿಯ ಇತರ ಮಕ್ಕಳಿಂದ ಅಸಭ್ಯ ವರ್ತನೆ
Hindi: Discrimination by other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste - ऊँची जाति के अन्य छात्रों द्वारा भेदभाव/दुर्व्यवहार किया जाता है
Tamil: Discrimination by other children/ Misbehaviour by other children from higher caste - பிற மாணவர்களால் பாகுபடுகாட்டப்படுதல்/ பிற உயர் சாதி மாணவர்கள் தவறாக நடத்தல்
